parent1.code: A captivating watercolor of a radiant, resplendent golden phoenix with iridescent, shimmering feathers in the intricate, sophisticated style of Art Nouveau. It magnificently flares its wings on the lush, verdant emerald meadow in the enchanted, mystical forest on a tranquil, misty morning, soaring gracefully above a vibrant, kaleidoscopic carpet of blooming wildflowers, amidst ancient, towering trees with gnarled, twisted branches adorned with ethereal, softly glowing runes.

parent2.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with shimmering feathers in the style of abstract art. It bursts into view above the crashing waves of an ancient shoreline at sunset, scattering glowing cinders from its tail amidst an environment of crumbling ruins and bioluminescent flora.

offspring.code: A stunning sketch of a majestic, gleaming golden phoenix with delicate, iridescent plumes in the elegant, whimsical style of fantasy art. It hovers gracefully above the crystal-clear waters of a serene, ancient lagoon under a starlit, twilight sky, casting reflections across the mirror-like surface. The scene is surrounded by bioluminescent corals and rare, luminescent aquatic plants, amidst crescent-shaped cliffs covered in luminescent moss, creating an enchanting atmosphere.
